description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Gatinho purrs with a rating of 80, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 160, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Leverage for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50802-16162-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [160 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
